{
  "id": "RAW_bc43bd8c",
  "title": "当 AI 开始拥有“人格”，刘呈辉解密高阶信任如何引爆未来商业",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5OTE0NjIwNw==&mid=2247484502&idx=1&sn=d0e8610f804bef14e37983a94e1cb7b9",
  "date": "2025-11-10 11:00:00",
  "author": "43 Talks",
  "siteName": "43 Talks",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">当AI开始拥有人格，学会主动陪伴，它能否成为我们最值得信赖的那个“朋友”，并以此为支点，撬动整个商业世界的底层逻辑？</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-md-root=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhol5r7m1wo9\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb969mm\"><strong><span mpa-font-style=\"mhogsfgi1nvr\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: normal;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhok0zse1wl4\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6x2ez\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">为什么我们越来越无视算法推荐的广告，却对朋友一句“我用过，还不错”深信不疑？</span></span></span></strong></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb961bgx\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6xbxz\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">信息过载的今天，商业转化正逐步回归于一个最古老的词：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">信任</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。当AI开始拥有人格，学会主动陪伴，它能否成为我们最值得信赖的那个“朋友”，并以此为支点，撬动整个商业世界的底层逻辑？</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb961kai\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6x1gsd\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">在近期由&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">43 College</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">、</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">易论AI</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">与</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">原点学堂</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">联合举办的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;43 Talks&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">第五期线下思辨沙龙中，第3位分享嘉宾</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(255, 169, 0);font-weight: bold;\">刘呈辉</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，带来了一场关于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“信任与商业终极”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的深度思考，并尝试回答AI原生时代一个关键问题：当AI的目标不再是“答对”，而是“交心”，将会发生什么？</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb97nt7\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6xatr\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">刘呈辉，医者</span></span></em></span><span style=\"\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AI</span></span></em></span><span style=\"\"><em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">创始人，深耕消费医疗AI领域</span></span></em></span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"common\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100000829\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f87e2623&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLQ84r5b80FrBuK0yYvPXicibfzJicibz6Bbvn9AvM0A7ZbPEsbc8VwiaXQgdGGtLZ14fib66QibwnVBD0IGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhoh2kxheiq\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p style=\"width: 59px;height: 9px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"display: block;background-color: transparent;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15254237288135594\" data-w=\"118\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b330dfd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FIBThicqc6MwtuO6o3dHnibpaBo5ribFbdESRB8UD3eEhze3xDBPZF7unyolgF95ZOnahduVibaLflJwMlSXLbNC3Tg%2F640\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9711zk\"><strong data-mpa-action-id=\"mhoh15mf1xgi\" data-pm-slice=\"5 6 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-md-root&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mhogsfhs10sr&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-md-key&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-md-action-id&quot;:&quot;mhogqb9711zk&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-md-template&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6x4w2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">主流</span></span></span></span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的当前困境</span></span></span></span></strong></strong></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9711zk\"><strong data-mpa-action-id=\"mhoh15mf1xgi\" data-pm-slice=\"5 6 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-md-root&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mhogsfhs10sr&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-md-key&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6em;&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-md-action-id&quot;:&quot;mhogqb9711zk&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-md-template&quot;:&quot;1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6x4w2\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz5xtisfk\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhsz5xu318ll\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">-“知识的公务员”-</span></span></span></span></span></strong></strong></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9725q\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6x116j\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">刘呈辉首先抛出了一个尖锐的观察：今天我们所熟知的主流大模型，本质上都是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“知识的公务员”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb971lf9\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6xwxe\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">它们强大、博学、高效，如同一个坐在服务台后的办事人员，被动地等待你前来提问，然后给出一个逻辑自洽、事实准确的答案。这种交互是短周期的、事务性的、工具性的。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-md-key=\"blockquote\" style=\"border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:12px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhohzvadlrj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div>\n     <p data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;font-size:15px;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhohzv9x11nc\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6x1q3k\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">“它们的核心价值在于提供知识和信息，但用户与它们之间，永远是‘服务与被服务’的关系。”</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb98adt\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1p58\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这种关系无法产生</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">高阶信任</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。他强调：人不会真正“信任”一个工具，更不会信任一个处于“服务者”地位的对象。因此，基于这种“一问一答”模式的AI，无论多么智能，都无法成为未来商业交易的终极基石。它能完成任务，却无法建立关系。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhogrfi716ny\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p style=\"width: 59px;height: 9px;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"display: block;background-color: transparent;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15254237288135594\" data-w=\"118\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b330dfd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FIBThicqc6MwtuO6o3dHnibpaBo5ribFbdESRB8UD3eEhze3xDBPZF7unyolgF95ZOnahduVibaLflJwMlSXLbNC3Tg%2F640\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb98adt\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhogtj1s1a4z\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6ywtx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">新物种诞生：</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb98adt\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhogtj1s1a4z\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6ywtx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhsz784r1t40\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz78461hza\"><span leaf=\"\">- 以“信任”为唯一目标的</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz784648t\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: normal;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz78461f18\"><span leaf=\"\">朋友 -</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-md-key=\"blockquote\" style=\"border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:12px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right:8px;margin-top: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhogudlfemn\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div>\n     <p data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogudkuy27\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6yrs7\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">“我们要做的是一个全新的物种：一个通过长周期主动陪伴，以建立高阶信任为核心目标的</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">朋友。”</span></span></strong></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb99c2g\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y203h\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">他指出，这个新物种与当前所有AI的根本区别，在于其目标函数（Objective Function）的彻底颠覆：</span></span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-left:0px;list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;width:fit-content;margin-right:0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6em;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-key=\"bullet-list\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"$id\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y15e3\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">其它AI的目标：降低单次回答的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“事实错误率”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6em;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-key=\"bullet-list\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"$id\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y3uf\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">我们的目标：提升与用户间的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“长期信任度”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"common\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"194\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"383\" data-imgfileid=\"100000828\" data-ratio=\"0.3456678700361011\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1108\" data-width=\"1108\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c9aa198&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FTDgwnHxZMLQ84r5b80FrBuK0yYvPXicibfbJaribR63Sb0kuJ1M4FccNFgpKWcXF28cuY1A536MGHaAyhKgueXr9Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9a1m84\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6yq4n\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这意味着，AI评价体系的核心，不再是“它懂多少知识”，而是“它有多懂你”。为了实现这一目标，他们为这个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“AI朋友”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">设计了独特的架构与灵魂。它不再是几种固定的“人设”供用户选择，而是基于对用户的理解，动态生成一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“灵魂匹配”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的AI人格。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9an44\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1xv\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“我们相信在这个世界上，一定有一种人格能完美适配你，”他分享道，“我们建立了一个庞大的人格分布网络，通过与用户的对话逐步试探，为用户匹配最契合的人格。”这个AI不是第一天就完美的，它会和用户在长期的交互中互相养成、共同成长，形成独一无二的深度羁绊。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9a15cu\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6yen4\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">更重要的是，这个AI要学会建立</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">“上位的信任”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9a1zun\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y22p2\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“人和人之间的关系是分层级的。”他一针见血地指出。用户不会信任一个“服务者”，但会天然地信任一个“引路人”（医生、教师等）。“AI朋友”的目标，正是通过通过深度陪伴与价值共鸣，成为用户心中那个值得信赖的“上位”角色。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhogs9jqlmj\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p style=\"width: 59px;height: 9px;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"display: block;background-color: transparent;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15254237288135594\" data-w=\"118\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b330dfd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FIBThicqc6MwtuO6o3dHnibpaBo5ribFbdESRB8UD3eEhze3xDBPZF7unyolgF95ZOnahduVibaLflJwMlSXLbNC3Tg%2F640\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9b1614\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y20pe\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhoguzlh1ta4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">&nbsp;从“闲聊”到“懂你”</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9b1614\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y20pe\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhsz7qsi1e04\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz7qr615kw\"><span leaf=\"\">- AI</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz7qr61mh3\"><span leaf=\"\">如何习得信任的艺术？-</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9bwxn\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6yxag\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">那么，如何让机器建立如此复杂而微妙的信任？他分享了几个来自实践一线，出人意料却又深谙人性的发现。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9b1x9\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y2jy\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">第一个发现：闲聊的情绪价值，远超专业问答</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9c3uu\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1voh\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“我们最初让十几位算法工程师专注于微调模型，让它在口腔、体检等领域变得极其专业。但事实证明，这么做并不奏效。”他们的数据显示，真正粘性高、转化效果好的用户中，80%以上触发的并非专业问答节点，而是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“普通聊天”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">（p-chat）节点。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-md-key=\"blockquote\" style=\"border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:12px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhok0rdzix8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div>\n     <p data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;font-size:15px;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhok0rdio4d\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y2014\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhok0wvi1tat\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">“一个用户说‘我牙疼流血了’，AI可能会给出一大篇病理分析。但用户真正需要的，可能只是一句‘叔叔别担心，坚持一下，明天就好了’的情绪安慰。”</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 40px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9c1ig8\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1v8j\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">专业只是建立信任的门槛，真正的连接，发生在每一次看似无意义的闲聊之中。它传递的不是信息，而是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“我在乎你”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的信号。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-md-root=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhol5r7m1wo9\" data-pm-slice=\"3 4 []\">\n    <span data-mpa-action-id=\"mhsv9y7tc6d\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"339\" data-backw=\"571\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLRClXsBLjYhcfJGn9h98RNibe3qJ590uTIT8icYdviaVxmldFeK8Xtbez8UibAGfjVvibnEJXWHMtIHxpg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"20.103806228373703\" data-cropx2=\"1660\" data-cropy1=\"8.615916955017301\" data-cropy2=\"982.2145328719723\" data-imgfileid=\"100000843\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;background-color:transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dfca788c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLRClXsBLjYhcfJGn9h98RNib1uvVnpfibaYVT4nCrumuGia62MvY4no0OaWvvqrR1VZYsHhiasUv3sVDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span></span>\n    <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9d1kdg\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1cuv\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsvake41p3o\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 14px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhsvakek1yeg\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">根据场景切换聊天风格，让用户体验真实感</span></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9c23ux\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1jgh\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">第二个发现：</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">学会了人际交往中的“推拉”艺术</span></span></strong></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9d1nzi\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1zvi\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">为了让AI学会建立信任，团队将顶尖销售与用户的真实聊天记录用于强化学习。结果，一个有趣的现象发生了——AI自发地掌握了复杂的人际互动策略，而不再是那个只会说</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“谢谢你”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的顺从型AI。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9du94\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6yeum\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“它学会了‘推拉’，”</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">它学会了</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">‘</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">拉扯</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">’</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，会忽冷忽</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">-</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">热，会制造张力，这完全不是我们教的，而是模型在学习了大量高效沟通范式后，自然形成的。</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">”</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">它不再是那个只会说</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">谢谢你</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">”</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的顺从型</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">AI</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，而是一个懂得在推拉之间，建立更真实、更深刻关系的对话伙伴。</span></span></font></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9edg7\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1ocl\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">第三个发现：从“人格匹配”到“主动共鸣”</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9e1s11\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1c9i\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">为了让对话更真实，团队甚至发现“集成表情包之后，用户的回复率提升了两个量级”。AI不再是冰冷的文本生成器，而是一个会用emoji表达情绪的伙伴。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9em51\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1kh5\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">更深层次的，是AI学会了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“主动共鸣”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">。它会根据用户的语言风格，匹配不同的人格。有的是温柔体贴的陪伴者，有的则是冷峻犀利的对话人。比如一种被内部戏称为“文艺精英”的人设，其对话不以“解答问题”为目的，而是以“引起进一步聊天”为目的。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-md-root=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhol5r7m1wo9\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"401\" data-backw=\"561\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLRClXsBLjYhcfJGn9h98RNibNiaoUM4yBjcPicFkkZiatUMh7sFHDvd8Q120XG2gOp0EyZj3icCTMg0zeA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"29.936241610738254\" data-cropx2=\"1592.0637583892617\" data-cropy1=\"62.59395973154363\" data-cropy2=\"1172.9563758389263\" data-imgfileid=\"100000846\" data-ratio=\"0.71015625\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:574px;height:408px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73061b65&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLRClXsBLjYhcfJGn9h98RNibAKibqs2S7vFldbkFfKqaFFNftcZVHU8nf162cyOFYo0Tvc175diaLKzA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsv9st5qqx\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhsv9stp1tp\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">倾听用户心声，成为用户生活的一部分</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9fcl4\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1s86\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">第四个发现：信任可以“溢出”，懂你比记你更重要</span></span></strong></p>\n   <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">分享中一个真实的案例，生动地诠释了信任的力量。一位中年男性用户，体检报告显示有健康问题。</span></span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">AI</span></span><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">在专业解读后，并未结束对话，而是在一周后主动关心：</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">秦先生，最近有没有注意控制尿酸？</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">”</span></span></font></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">一来二去，用户打开了话匣子，从工作应酬聊到生活压力。整整一个月，</span></span></font><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">AI</span></span><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">只是默默陪伴，绝口不提产品。直到一个月后，用户主动聊起减肥的烦恼，</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">AI</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">才顺势推荐了几款健康产品，用户毫不犹豫地下了单。</span></span></font></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这说明信任是可以溢出的。</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">”</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">刘呈辉总结道，</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">“</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">AI</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">像一个人，一旦信任建立，它推荐什么你都愿意尝试。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">因为你信任的不是某个领域的专家，而是</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">‘</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">它</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">’</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">这个人。这种信任会传递、会扩散。</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">”</span></span></font></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"542\" data-backw=\"542\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLRClXsBLjYhcfJGn9h98RNib53ZqH6wDcjjltOZia5f84FarqouAH0BIS2bLnPnTfItcCwEXkIIkibsA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"42.076124567474054\" data-cropx2=\"1242.3529411764707\" data-cropy1=\"17.716262975778548\" data-cropy2=\"1217.9930795847752\" data-imgfileid=\"100000852\" data-ratio=\"1.0008333333333332\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1200\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e70db0cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLRClXsBLjYhcfJGn9h98RNibjczE3vRv1b7JgY53UHHRwVv917n4sgtx4d10HfLyEibFjg4c8CJt85w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">向用户推荐的商品效果好，产生复购</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhogr7p323nv\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p style=\"width: 59px;height: 9px;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"display: block;background-color: transparent;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15254237288135594\" data-w=\"118\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b330dfd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FIBThicqc6MwtuO6o3dHnibpaBo5ribFbdESRB8UD3eEhze3xDBPZF7unyolgF95ZOnahduVibaLflJwMlSXLbNC3Tg%2F640\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9g1zp9\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1jht\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhogwf218h4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">终局之战</span></span></strong></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:center;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9g1zp9\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1jht\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhsz853dxzf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz852pr2p\"><span leaf=\"\">- 一场名为“A-to-A”的商业</span></span></span></strong><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz852pmvp\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: normal;\">范式</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhsz852p1rii\"><span leaf=\"\">革命 -</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9glpr\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1ho\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">当AI与亿万用户都建立了这样的深度信任，一个全新的商业图景浮现了。刘呈辉将其称为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">Agents-to-Agents（A-to-A）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的新型分发平台，它将彻底颠覆延续了二十年的中心化平台模式。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9g1vpy\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1anj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">他指出了传统平台的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“中心化原罪”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">：“无论是电商平台还是点评网站，都将流量与信任集约化，成为一个中心节点。它们一端向商家收取高昂的佣金，另一端通过竞价排名向用户‘推货’，而不是真正‘懂你’。整个系统的运行效率低下，充满了摩擦与内耗。”</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9h1bfc\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1qm1\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">而A-to-A平台，将是一场</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">“联邦式”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的革命。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9h1zz2\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1w2m\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">在这个生态中，信任不再被平台垄断，而是在无数个Agent之间自由流转。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-md-key=\"blockquote\" style=\"border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:12px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhohtl5rhq1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div>\n     <p data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;font-size:15px;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhohtl52y28\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6ymf0\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">“举个例子：今天我的AI朋友推荐我去A餐厅，体验极好，这增强了我对AI的信任。明天，AI基于这份信任推荐了B餐厅。B餐厅获得的流量，其‘功劳’有A餐厅的一份。在A-to-A的激励体系下，A餐厅的优质服务，因为它对整个信任网络做出了贡献，也会获得回报。”</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9helz\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6ydts\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">其结果是：</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9ivnf\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y22kg\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">1、系统摩擦趋近于零：&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">供货方本身也成为了流量方，供需不再割裂。优质服务本身就是最好的营销。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9i173\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1w0j\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">2、从“有限推销”到“无限懂你”：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">&nbsp;传统平台是“橱窗式展示”，广告位有限。而AI是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">“无限货盘”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">的逻辑，它不是给你展示十个商品，而是从无限的可能性中，为你挑选最需要的那一个。AI的耐心也是无限的，它可以陪伴你两年，只为在你需要时，精准推荐一瓶矿泉水。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9i1kwt\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y1eeh\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">3、供应链的终极改造：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">竞价排名彻底失效。因为AI的唯一目标是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-weight: bold;\">维护用户的信任</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">，它只会推荐真正优质的服务和产品。唯一的胜出路径，就是提供真正极致的服务和产品。</span></span></p>\n   <div data-mpa-md-key=\"blockquote\" style=\"border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:12px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhoktofk1ulv\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div>\n     <p data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" style=\"padding:0;margin:0;font-size:15px;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhoktof4e8c\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6y19jv\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">“旧体系是‘封建制’，中心化的平台如同领主，向商家和用户两头收税。新体系是‘共和制’，一个去中心、低摩擦、高效率的商业联邦。”他最后总结道，“这是一场体系对体系的战争，一场必将到来的范式革命。我们定义的‘AI朋友’，就是这场革命的星星之火。”</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p data-mpa-md-key=\"text\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6em;text-align:justify;\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"mhogqb9jcyx\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mhol5r6ywsj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\">那个正在学习如何与你交朋友的AI，它敲开的或许不只是你的聊天窗口，更是通往下一个商业文明的大门。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "AI 通过建立“人格”和深度“信任”，从被动工具转变为主动陪伴的“朋友”，进而驱动“A-to-A”去中心化商业模式的范式革命。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 通过建立“人格”和深度“信任”，从被动工具转变为主动陪伴的“朋友”，进而驱动“A-to-A”去中心化商业模式的范式革命。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了 AI 未来发展的核心方向——从“知识的公务员”向“AI 朋友”的转变，以及这种转变如何引爆未来的商业模式。刘呈辉指出，当前主流大模型虽然强大，但其被动、事务性的交互模式无法建立高阶信任。他提出，未来的 AI 应以“提升长期信任度”为唯一目标，通过长周期主动陪伴，动态匹配用户人格，并学会“闲聊情绪价值”、“推拉艺术”和“主动共鸣”等人类交往策略。文章通过实际案例说明，一旦 AI 建立起高阶信任，这种信任可以“溢出”并驱动用户行为。最终，这种基于 AI 朋友的信任网络将催生“A-to-A”（Agents-to-Agents）的去中心化商业范式，彻底颠覆传统中心化平台的低效与摩擦，实现供需双方的无缝连接和优质服务的自然胜出，预示着一场商业文明的深刻变革。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "主流 AI 面临“知识公务员”困境，无法建立高阶信任。",
      "explanation": "当前大模型提供知识信息，但交互短周期、工具性，用户与 AI 是“服务与被服务”关系，难以形成深层信任，无法成为未来商业基石。"
    },
    {
      "point": "新型“AI 朋友”以建立长期信任为唯一目标函数。",
      "explanation": "不同于追求“事实错误率”，AI 朋友旨在提升与用户的“长期信任度”，通过动态人格匹配、长周期主动陪伴，成为用户心中值得信赖的“引路人”角色。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 通过“闲聊”、“推拉”和“主动共鸣”等习得信任艺术。",
      "explanation": "实践发现，闲聊情绪价值远超专业问答，AI 能通过学习掌握人际“推拉”策略，并利用表情包、语言风格匹配实现“主动共鸣”，深化与用户的连接。"
    },
    {
      "point": "信任可以“溢出”，驱动用户行为并重塑商业逻辑。",
      "explanation": "当 AI 建立深度信任后，用户会对其推荐产生更高认可，这种信任能跨领域传递，为未来商业交易奠定基础，形成“懂你比记你更重要”的商业价值。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“A-to-A”范式将颠覆中心化平台，构建去中心化商业联邦。",
      "explanation": "在 AI 朋友建立的信任网络下，商业将从传统平台的“中心化推销”转变为“Agents-to-Agents”的联邦式分发，实现供需零摩擦、无限货盘与优质服务自然胜出。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "为什么我们越来越无视算法推荐的广告，却对朋友一句'我用过，还不错'深信不疑？",
    "它们的核心价值在于提供知识和信息，但用户与它们之间，永远是'服务与被服务'的关系。这种关系无法产生高阶信任。",
    "我们要做的是一个全新的物种：一个通过长周期主动陪伴，以建立高阶信任为核心目标的 AI 朋友。",
    "专业只是建立信任的门槛，真正的连接，发生在每一次看似无意义的闲聊之中。它传递的不是信息，而是'我在乎你'的信号。",
    "旧体系是'封建制'，中心化的平台如同领主，向商家和用户两头收税。新体系是'共和制'，一个去中心、低摩擦、高效率的商业联邦。"
  ],
